description: Every tourist coming to Prague has to visit the Wenceslas Square. It is full of impressive buildings underlining the beauty of our country. And every gay tourist will see that it is overcrowded with nice boys. I must admit that most of them are tourists. Often from other countries. But if you are open and talkative like me you will easily find a nice Czech boy there as well. Actually I already wanted to give up for that day when I finally met this youngster. He was so afraid and he looked so innocent that I had to try my best to persuade this handy student to make him my toy-boy for the night.
title: Czech Hunter 82
